---
title: Carb Smart Dill Pickle Chicken Breast Salad with Croutons and Dill Pickle Cream
description: Another chicken salad, you say?! But this isn't just any chicken salad. Dill pickle cream dolloped over BBQ-seasoned chicken livens up this full plate of veggies. Quick, simple and delicious!

